data.description: Huge price reduction!! Pond Lot, Amazing Amenities, New Paint, New Roof, New Tankless Hot water heater with HALO, New flooring throughout downstairs and New HVAC! This home is move in ready! Situated in the desirable Spring Grove Plantation, this property is a gem you don't want to miss. As you step inside the front door, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting foyer with dining room to the left, complete with gleaming NEW engineered hardwood floors and plenty of natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends.Off to the right of the living room is a great flex area that can be used for a playroom, 6th bedroom or office. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample countertop space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or simply preparing a meal for yourself, this kitchen has everything you need to make cooking a breeze. The spacious master suite located upstairs is a private oasis, featuring tray ceilings and an ensuite with double vanities, soaking tub and walk in shower. The master also has a large walk-in closet with an additional half door leading to tons of attic space. Also located upstairs are 4 additional bedrooms. One of the rooms does not have a closet so could be utilized as a bedroom or a large bonus space. The upstairs also features a full bath and oversized laundry room with folding counter. Outside enjoy your mornings on your back screened porch while enjoying the beautiful pond views. The additional extended patio space makes entertaining a breeze. Spring Grove features several community parks, soccer field, pool, disk golf and so much more! Come check out this home before its gone!
